{
  "texts": [
    "• It may be worth investigating the weak performance of ChatGPT in the domains of geometry, probability, and inequality that were observed in this study.",
    "• Additionally, one could examine how the utilization of ChatGPT for mathematics pre-learning by students affects their subsequent learning at school.",
    "• Finally, the impact of ChatGPT on students' cognitive and affective behaviors could be investigated.",
    "Author contributions: All authors have sufficiently contributed to the study and agreed with the results and conclusions.",
    "Funding: No funding source is reported for this study."
  ]
}